reviewText: My sister bought these at a yard sale and the went through  two generations,noe my nefew wants them for his family. Why aren't  they on disc yet?

Hey, what's not to love about a cartoon where a group of (literal) cow boys can be seen herding THEIR OWN KIND into a corral?  Guess the cartoon's producers didn't think that analogy through too thoroughly, and I suspect that perhaps it has something to do with why this series hasn't been released on DVD or Blu-ray yet.
